Website and its creation. Internet marketing and website. Wordpress. Google Analytics. Search Engine Optimization. Web analytics. Content marketing. Integrity.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to provide basic knowledge of website creation and management, search engine optimization and web analytics, and to relate the above to content marketing, so that learners can create discoverable and relatable web pages.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) knows and be able to compile the initial task of a website, which is in line with an internet marketing strategy;  2) knows internet marketing tools;  3) knows the possibilities of the free content management system Wordpress;  4) understands the role of search engine optimization; 5) knows the possibilities of web analytics;  6) is able to create a simpler website with the necessary attachments;  7) is able to create content for websites;  8) knows and be able to apply the basic principles of content marketing;  9) understand the integration of a website and its various parts with marketing and be able to monitor the necessary connections in order to ensure integrity;  10) is able to optimize a website for a search engine;  11) is able to use the basic tools of Google Analytics for web analytics.
